(1) Columns
------------
==> Learn how to modify columns with a handful of options for alignment, ordering, and offsetting thanks to our flexbox grid system. Plus, see how to use column classes to manage widths of non-grid elements.


(2) Vertical alignment [for .row parent]
-----------------------------------------

    <div class="container">
      <div class="row align-items-start">
	<div class="col bg-primary">Col1</div>
	<div class="col bg-danger">Col2</div>
	<div class="col bg-success">Col3</div>
      </div>
    </div>


    <div class="container">
      <div class="row align-items-center">
        <div class="col bg-primary">Col1</div>
        <div class="col bg-danger">Col2</div>
        <div class="col bg-success">Col3</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row align-items-end">
        <div class="col bg-primary">Col1</div>
        <div class="col bg-danger">Col2</div>
        <div class="col bg-success">Col3</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    
(3) Vertical Self alignment [for .row childrens]
-------------------------------------------------

    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col bg-primary align-self-start">Col1</div>
        <div class="col bg-danger align-self-center">Col2</div>
        <div class="col bg-success align-self-end">Col3</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    
(4) Horizontal Alignment [for .row parent]
-----------------------------------------

    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-start">
        <div class="col-3 bg-primary">Col1</div>
        <div class="col-3 bg-danger">Col2</div>
        <div class="col-3 bg-success">Col3</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-3 bg-primary">Col1</div>
        <div class="col-3 bg-danger">Col2</div>
        <div class="col-3 bg-success">Col3</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-end">
        <div class="col-3 bg-primary">Col1</div>
        <div class="col-3 bg-danger">Col2</div>
        <div class="col-3 bg-success">Col3</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-around">
        <div class="col-3 bg-primary">Col1</div>
        <div class="col-3 bg-danger">Col2</div>
        <div class="col-3 bg-success">Col3</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-between">
        <div class="col-3 bg-primary">Col1</div>
        <div class="col-3 bg-danger">Col2</div>
        <div class="col-3 bg-success">Col3</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-evenly">
        <div class="col-3 bg-primary">Col1</div>
        <div class="col-3 bg-danger">Col2</div>
        <div class="col-3 bg-success">Col3</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    
(5) Column breaks
------------------

    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-6 col-sm-4">.col-6 .col-sm-4</div>
        <div class="col-6 col-sm-4">.col-6 .col-sm-4</div>
        <!-- Force next columns to break to new line at md breakpoint and up -->
        <div class="w-100 d-none d-md-block"></div>
        <div class="col-6 col-sm-4">.col-6 .col-sm-4</div>
        <div class="col-6 col-sm-4">.col-6 .col-sm-4</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    
(6) Order classes [from 1 to 5]
-------------------------------

    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col order-3">col-1</div>
        <div class="col order-1">col-2</div>
        <div class="col order-2">col-3</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col order-last">col-1</div>
        <div class="col order-first">col-2</div>
        <div class="col order-2">col-3</div>
      </div>
    </div>


(7) Offset ( offset-[0-12]] Or [offset-[sm|md|lg|xl|xxl]-[0-12] )
------------

    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-2 offset-3">col-1</div>
        <div class="col-3">col-2</div>
        <div class="col-4">col-3</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-2 offset-lg-3 bg-primary">col-1</div>
        <div class="col-3">col-2</div>
        <div class="col-4">col-3</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    
(8) Margin utilities ([mr|ml]-auto) Or ([ml|mr]-[sm|md|lg|xl|xxl]-auto)
---------------------

    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-2 ml-auto bg-primary">col-1</div>
        <div class="col-3">col-2</div>
        <div class="col-4">col-3</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-2 mr-auto bg-primary">col-1</div>
        <div class="col-3">col-2</div>
        <div class="col-4">col-3</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-2 mr-md-auto bg-primary">col-1</div>
        <div class="col-3">col-2</div>
        <div class="col-4">col-3</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    
(9) clearfix
-------------

    <div class="clearfix">
      <img src="./gulp.png" class="col-6 ml-3 float-right" />

